{"type": "article", "id": 5782, "title": "墙面装饰丘", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-02T07:40:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233954hYklnXiSpoF3J1z7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t毕业于清华大学美术学院陶瓷艺术设计系的张民，毕业之后一直以陶瓷、玻璃等材料进行艺术设计创作。这款名为「丘」的墙面装饰，设计灵感源自张民的一次沙漠旅行，他打破了传统陶瓷的拼贴方式，将陶瓷制作成浮雕的凸起感，可以在不同光线下呈现不同的视觉效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233953WsH2UaClwKqPBy8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233953hwn3aVHYqzLxCT8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}